@startuml create-user-process-flow
participant User
participant CreateUser
participant API
participant Snackbar

User -> CreateUser : Enter details in form fields
CreateUser -> CreateUser : Validate form input
alt Passwords do not match
    CreateUser -> Snackbar : Show "Passwords do not match!"
else Valid input
    User -> CreateUser : Click "Create User"
    CreateUser -> API : Send POST request to /api/register
    alt Success response
        API -> CreateUser : Return success
        CreateUser -> Snackbar : Show "User created successfully!"
        CreateUser -> CreateUser : Clear form fields
    else Error response
        API -> CreateUser : Return error
        CreateUser -> Snackbar : Show "Error creating user. Please try again."
    end
end
@enduml
